reviews.review_text: This Show was so much fun, thanks, its a 3 plus but I hate atng I also hate five point scales but it is what it is. I remember how fun these were, the volleyball before the shows, the rise of jerry after the coma interruption, the park outside the show, the scene there with lake merritt, the whole deal. College! we all should have such an opportunity to go to college and do this! If I realized how lucky I was when I was standing there at this show i'd have valued it more. I'll be mean and give it a 3 but here is a lot going on in their minds at this, so maybe its a 3.85985 Thanks CM etc.
